<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们刚搬进白房子时，经常谈起爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们总是问关于爸爸的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是慢慢地，他们发现这些问题会让妈妈不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，他们就不再问了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，妈妈在忙碌地工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比把茶端到妈妈的“办公室”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房间里没有什么家具，只有一张桌子、一把椅子和一块地毯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但孩子们总会在窗台上放一瓶花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈说：“你们都很听话，特别是你，鲍比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>给我摘花、给我刷鞋、给我整理床铺……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比以前还怀疑过妈妈不知道他们的付出。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没什么。”鲍比虽然这么说，但是她很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈同意给每个孩子一小片花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们可以种他们想种的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯种了花，它们看上去像杂草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但菲利斯相信，它们总有一天会开花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得在他的花园里撒了蔬菜种子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有胡萝卜、洋葱和大头菜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是蔬菜从没长出来过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为彼得用泥土为玩具士兵做了堡垒和运河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比在她的花园里种了很多玫瑰花，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但新长出来的叶子都是棕色的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她希望这些玫瑰不会死。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，帕克斯来看花园。他劝鲍比烧掉她的玫瑰花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比，把它们挖出来烧掉！”帕克斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的花园里有玫瑰，我送给你一些。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，鲍比开始挖玫瑰，然后把它们扔到花园的另一边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比扔完回来，看到彼得在用她的耙子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耙子我正在用呢！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也正在用呢！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是是我先拿的！”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在轮到我了！”彼得说。于是他们俩开始吵架。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你总会为一些小事生气。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我先拿到耙子的。”鲍比抓着耙子不放，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天早上我明明说过我要用的。我说了吧，菲利斯？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“菲利斯，回答呀！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但菲利斯还是没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我有一个兄弟，而不是两个姐妹。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她想起自己要努力做个好孩子，于是就放开了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为彼得一直在用力，所以鲍比一放开，他就摔倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得在地上静静躺了一分钟，这让鲍比慌了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐起来，然后他突然尖叫了一声，又躺下不停地哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈跑出来，蹲在彼得身边问：“怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比和彼得都在拉耙子。”菲利斯回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比一放手，彼得就摔倒了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“彼得，别哭了。”妈妈说，“你受伤了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我的脚破了，太疼了。”彼得脸色苍白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他受伤了。他昏过去了。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她解开彼得的靴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在脱右脚的时候，有东西从他的脚上滴下来——是血。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>耙子的底部刺进了彼得的脚，脚在流血。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈把他抱回家，菲利斯跑去找医生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>